Market Dynamics
The savory snacks market is influenced by several key dynamics:
•	Rising Demand for Convenience Foods: The increasing preference for on-the-go snacking options has significantly boosted the demand for savory snacks. Consumers are seeking products that are easy to consume and provide a quick energy boost.
•	Health Consciousness: There is a growing trend towards healthier snacking habits, leading manufacturers to introduce low-fat, gluten-free, organic, and protein-rich savory snacks. These healthier options are rapidly gaining popularity among health-conscious consumers.
•	Technological Innovations: Advances in food processing technology have enabled the creation of novel textures, flavors, and packaging, enhancing consumer appeal and expanding product offerings.
