Market Segments
The savory snacks market can be segmented based on several factors:
•	By Product Type: The market includes potato chips, extruded snacks, nuts and seeds, popcorn, meat snacks, and others. Potato chips currently hold the largest market share due to their popularity and versatility.
•	By Category: Snacks are categorized into baked, fried, and others, with baked snacks accounting for the largest share due to consumer preferences for healthier options.
•	By Distribution Channel: Sales occur through supermarkets/hypermarkets, specialty stores, online stores, convenience stores, and others. Supermarkets/hypermarkets dominate the market due to their widespread presence and consumer convenience.
•	By Region: The market is analyzed across regions such as North America, Asia Pacific, Europe, Latin America, and Middle East and Africa. Asia Pacific is a significant market due to its large consumer base and growing demand for healthier snacks.
